.TH SL(1),User Commands,SL(1)

.SH sl - steam locomotive

.SH SYNOPSIS
sl

.SH DESCRIPTION
sl displays an ASCII art steam locomotive animating across the screen from right to left. The train consists of a locomotive with animated wheels, a coal tender, and a passenger car.

.SH EXAMPLES

$ sl

(a steam locomotive scrolls across the screen)

.SH NOTES
sl takes no arguments. It runs until the train has fully passed off the left edge of the screen.
